<v-app class="appContainer">

    class="newform"
    :model="ruleForm1"

    ref="ruleForm1"
    lazy-validation

        v-model="ruleForm1.project_name"

    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item>
      <el-button class="successB" @click="create('ruleForm1')">Create project</el-button>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
</v-app>
